# Git LFS routing for the in-repo Theoryâ†”Computation book (cookbook/book/).
#
# The book commits its emitted artifacts once and reads them forever: the
# small-subset goldens every chapter asserts against (~77 MB of Parquet) and
# the H2 scale tier â€” the ~170kĂ—768 ogbn-arxiv embedding corpus, the held-out
# query vectors, and the frozen ANN sidecar bundle (~982 MB, .usearch/.rowmap/
# .parquet). These are large binary blobs that drift the git object store if
# packed inline, so they live in Git LFS, off the object store. The small
# JSON/txt sidecars (manifests, golden metrics, checksums, id lists) stay as
# plain tracked text and are NOT routed here.
cookbook/book/artifacts/**/*.parquet  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
cookbook/book/artifacts/**/*.usearch  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
cookbook/book/artifacts/**/*.rowmap   filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
